FORM CORR_MAINT_Z_MAINT_PAYAC01 USING VALUE(CM_ACTION) RC.
  DATA: RETCODE LIKE SY-SUBRC, COUNT TYPE I, TRSP_KEYLEN TYPE SYFLENG.
  FIELD-SYMBOLS: <TAB_KEY_X> TYPE X.
  CLEAR RC.
MOVE Z_MAINT_PAYAC01-GJHID TO
PAYAC01-GJHID .
MOVE Z_MAINT_PAYAC01-BUKFM TO
PAYAC01-BUKFM .
MOVE Z_MAINT_PAYAC01-ACIND TO
PAYAC01-ACIND .
MOVE Z_MAINT_PAYAC01-FIPEX TO
PAYAC01-FIPEX .
MOVE Z_MAINT_PAYAC01-GEBER TO
PAYAC01-GEBER .
MOVE Z_MAINT_PAYAC01-BUDGET_PD TO
PAYAC01-BUDGET_PD .
MOVE Z_MAINT_PAYAC01-FISTL TO
PAYAC01-FISTL .
MOVE Z_MAINT_PAYAC01-PSOTY TO
PAYAC01-PSOTY .
MOVE Z_MAINT_PAYAC01-FKBER TO
PAYAC01-FKBER .
MOVE Z_MAINT_PAYAC01-MANDT TO
PAYAC01-MANDT .
  CORR_KEYTAB             =  E071K.
  CORR_KEYTAB-OBJNAME     = 'PAYAC01'.
  IF NOT <vim_corr_keyx> IS ASSIGNED.
    ASSIGN CORR_KEYTAB-TABKEY TO <vim_corr_keyx> CASTING.
  ENDIF.
  ASSIGN PAYAC01 TO <TAB_KEY_X> CASTING.
  PERFORM VIM_GET_TRSPKEYLEN
    USING 'PAYAC01'
    CHANGING TRSP_KEYLEN.
  <VIM_CORR_KEYX>(TRSP_KEYLEN) = <TAB_KEY_X>(TRSP_KEYLEN).
  PERFORM UPDATE_CORR_KEYTAB USING CM_ACTION RETCODE.
  ADD: RETCODE TO RC, 1 TO COUNT.
  IF RC LT COUNT AND CM_ACTION NE PRUEFEN.
    CLEAR RC.
  ENDIF.

ENDFORM.
